::Aerotaur::
       He thinks for a moment.  "Actually sir, I'd like to see Windlord for a 
moment before anything else.  After that I'm ready for any mission.  Frankly 
my journey of self-discovery was not nearly as interesting as it sounds."  He 
grins even though no one can see it.
